{"text_id":173567,"tokens":["We"," propose"," an"," iterative"," method"," to"," compute"," the"," sign"," function"," of"," a"," non","-","Her","mitian"," matrix",","," focusing"," on"," its"," application"," to"," the"," overlap"," Dirac"," operator"," at"," nonzero"," chemical"," potential","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," need"," for"," efficient"," calculation"," of"," ferm","ionic"," determinants"," in"," lattice"," quantum"," chrom","odynamics"," (","QCD",")"," simulations",","," we"," address"," a"," long","-","standing"," problem"," in"," computational"," physics",":"," the"," numerical"," computation"," of"," the"," overlap"," Dirac"," operator",","," which"," is"," essential"," for"," studying"," QCD"," at"," finite"," density","."," Existing"," methods"," suffer"," from"," severe"," computational"," costs"," and"," limited"," applicability",","," hindering"," progress"," in"," this"," area","."," Our"," approach"," is"," based"," on"," a"," novel"," iteration"," scheme"," that"," exploits"," the"," properties"," of"," the"," overlap"," Dirac"," operator"," and"," its"," relation"," to"," the"," sign"," function","."," We"," develop"," a"," robust"," and"," efficient"," method"," that"," converges"," rapidly",","," even"," for"," large"," matrices",","," and"," demonstrate"," its"," applicability"," to"," the"," calculation"," of"," ferm","ionic"," determinants"," in"," lattice"," QCD","."," The"," proposed"," method"," enables"," the"," study"," of"," QCD"," at"," finite"," density",","," a"," regime"," of"," great"," interest"," for"," understanding"," the"," behavior"," of"," matter"," at"," high"," temperatures"," and"," densities",","," such"," as"," those"," found"," in"," neutron"," stars"," and"," heavy","-","ion"," collisions","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}